query:
INSERT INTO market_order_latest
            (
                touched,
                structure_id,
                region_id,
                order_id,

                type_id,
                remaining,
                price,
                expires,
                is_buy
            )
            SELECT TRUE, $1, $2, * FROM UNNEST(
                $3::BIGINT[],
                $4::INTEGER[],
                $5::INTEGER[],
                $6::FLOAT[],
                $7::TIMESTAMP[],
                $8::BOOLEAN[]
            )
            ON CONFLICT (order_id)
            DO UPDATE SET
                remaining = EXCLUDED.remaining,
                expires = EXCLUDED.expires,
                price = EXCLUDED.price,
                touched = TRUE
